Author: Collin Watson
Message:
chore(project): add gitleaks for secret and PII detection

Replace the filename-based reject-secrets pre-commit hook with gitleaks,
which scans staged file contents for secrets, API keys, and PII (emails,
phone numbers, SSNs, IP addresses). Managed as a mise dependency.

Also fix commit-msg hook to use lefthook v2 {1} template for the
commit message file path instead of shell $1.

feat(project): add M1-M3 codebase

Implements three milestones of the Hexorder game system design tool:
- M1: Hex grid rendering, orthographic camera, terrain painting
- M2: Game System container, cell types with properties, editor UI
- M3: Unit types, unit placement/movement/deletion, unit inspector

Includes feature specs, contracts, research docs, and build scripts.
71 tests pass, clippy clean.
